OL,3,CHospital at highest alert level due to
OL,4,C'significant demand'
OL,6,FThe NHS trust that runs the Royal
OL,7,FLancaster Infirmary has declared its
OL,8,Fhighest level of alert due to
OL,9,F"significant and growing demand".
OL,11,FThe University Hospitals of Morecambe
OL,12,FBay NHS Foundation Trust says it has
OL,13,Fescalated to Operational Pressures
OL,14,FEscalation Level (OPEL) 4 - the
OL,15,Fhighest alert within a hospital - to
OL,16,Fhelp cope with the increased pressures.
OL,18,FOPEL 4 is only declared when a
OL,19,Fhospital is "unable to deliver
OL,20,Fcomprehensive care" and patient safety
OL,21,Fis at risk.
