OL,3,CHospital at highest alert level due to
OL,4,C'significant demand'
OL,6,FA spokesperson from the hospital said:
OL,7,F"As always, patient safety must take
OL,8,Fpriority and we need to take action to
OL,9,Fmake sure that those who are more
OL,10,Fclinically urgent get the help they
OL,11,Fneed as quickly as possible."
OL,13,FOther measures are being taken by the
OL,14,Fhospital, including cancelling non-
OL,15,Fessential meetings to redirect
OL,16,Fclinicians' time to helping patients,
OL,17,Fand using alternative options to the
OL,18,FEmergency Department.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
