OL,3,CHospital at highest alert level due to
OL,4,C'significant demand'
OL,6,FThe trust has urged patients to
OL,7,Fcontinue to turn up for appointments,
OL,8,Funless they have been contacted
OL,9,Fdirectly, and to contact the hospital
OL,10,Fif they are unable to make them.
OL,12,FIt added: "Our teams continue to work
OL,13,Fexceptionally hard; and we would like
OL,14,Fto reassure our patients and the
OL,15,Fpublic that in spite of the challenges
OL,16,Ffaced, essential services remain fully
OL,17,Fopen for anyone who needs them so if
OL,18,Fyou require urgent medical help,
OL,19,Fplease continue to come forward.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
