OL,3,CHospital at highest alert level due to
OL,4,C'significant demand'
OL,6,F"The public can help us manage these
OL,7,Fperiods of demand by ensuring they are
OL,8,Fseeking help from the most appropriate
OL,9,Fhealth services, and only attending
OL,10,FA&E for serious accidents and
OL,11,Femergencies.
OL,13,F"If you are unwell, visit NHS 111
OL,14,Fonline for 24/7 advice about the most
OL,15,Fappropriate care for your needs."
